The [Laboratory of Excellence LABEX UCN@Sophia](http://www.ucnlab.eu/) provides scholarships to highly ranked students wishing to pursue studies at PhD level after the Ubinet master.

The conditions to get this grant are the following:

* Excellent academic records
* Have obtained a Bachelor diploma (or equivalent) from a foreign University
* Follow a 2nd Year Master Program at the University Nice Sophia Antipolis.
* Do the internship in one of the LABEX's research teams
* Be eager to pursue PhD studies in one of the [LABEX's research domains](https://www.ucnlab.eu/node/5).

Other grants program are available, depending upon your home country. Below we list some of these programs:

- [Eiffel](http://www.campusfrance.org/en/eiffel) applicable to all foreign students; deadline: first week of January.
